{"tid":1085960,"cid":21,"subCid":3,"title":"有冇人聽スピッツ Spitz (2)","createTime":"2019-03-31T14:20:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-24T05:30:11.000Z","uid":172042,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d7c1a72e1a7393fda41f2d05fca3d304119852fd","tid":1085960,"uid":172042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T14:20:15.000Z","msg":"全員1967年出生、身高167cm（聲稱），1987年組隊，1991年主流出道<br />\n4月1號有新歌！NHK晨間劇「なつぞら」主題曲「優しいあの子」<br />\n上次個post沉咗所以開過個<br />\n<br />\n官網 <a href=\"https://spitz-web.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fspitz-web.com&d=Sk6y7wLkZ8LsH37jlkaP934HMPoqNxaa4E9h32y1mRE%3D&h=91f07cf3\" target=\"_blank\">https://spitz-web.com</a><br />\n官方youtube channel <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/user/spitzclips\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fuser%2Fspitzclips&d=Sk6y7wLkZ8LsH37jlkaP934HMPoqNxaa4E9h32y1mRE%3D&h=fbfe7b91\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/user/spitzclips</a><br />\n電台節目 Spitz 草野マサムネのロック大陸漫遊記 <a href=\"https://www.tfm.co.jp/manyuki/index.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tfm.co.jp%2Fmanyuki%2Findex.php&d=Sk6y7wLkZ8LsH37jlkaP934HMPoqNxaa4E9h32y1mRE%3D&h=e0ebd3fc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.tfm.co.jp/manyuki/index.php</a><br />\nTokyo FM 日本時間每週日21:00~21:55<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">海外要用vpn聽</span></span><br />\n<br />\nQ&amp;A<br />\nQ1: 佢哋除咗ロビンソン、チェリー、楓同空も飛べるはず之外仲有乜歌？<br />\nA1: 可以上官網搵discography或者不妨上youtube發掘下<br />\n<br />\nQ2: 幾時會有演唱會？點樣買到飛睇？<br />\nA2: 通常每年夏季都會有三個events，大阪ロックロックこんにちは、東京新木場sunset、仙台ロックのほそ道，要抽飛，仙台好似易啲（唔係日本在住唔使諗新木場，講起就把幾火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）；hall tour要等佢哋出大碟先會有消息，好難抽不過佢哋本人唔鼓勵買黃牛；arena tour會易啲但係理論上隔幾年先開一次；仲有fc tour咁唔係會員當然冇得抽<br />\n<br />\nQ3: 點樣知最新消息？<br />\nA3: twitter follow spimo會快啲知"},{"pid":"cfb1cd0a3cdf9c536ea0c2cf7e0a75648b12bf60","tid":1085960,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime"